properties.value: You cut into your arm with the Knife of Sacrifices. The pain is excruciating. Shaking, you manage to collect some of your blood in a small vial. The knife quickly raises in temperature until it disintegrates. Your wound then begins to close itself, leaving no trace at all besides a warm feeling throughout your body.
